# ─── Per-user / runtime state (never commit) ─────────────────────────────
# Sprint 05 taste profile, Sprint 06 traces, pre-Sprint-05 legacy file.
# Default storage is ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_DATA} (v1.5.1+), out of the project
# tree — these patterns still apply for legacy in-repo setups, opt-in via
# VISIONARY_TASTE_IN_REPO=1, and dev/test fallbacks. Opt out fully with
# VISIONARY_DISABLE_TASTE=1 / VISIONARY_NO_TRACES=1 — see docs/taste-privacy.md.
#
# Sprint 16-24 (v1.6.0) caches all flow under .visionary-cache/ already:
#   .visionary-cache/photo-cache/<sha256>.bin    (Sprint 18 from-photo)
#   .visionary-cache/audio-cache/                (Sprint 19 from-track, if used)
#   .visionary-cache/voice-rec/<id>.{webm,wav}   (Sprint 22 voice mic recordings)
# Sprint 21B coined-styles persist in taste/coined-styles.jsonl (covered).
# Sprint 23 patina reads git blame at runtime — no local state to ignore.
.visionary-cache/
.visionary/
.visionary-runtime/
taste/
coined-styles/
system.md

# Claude Code agent worktrees — created by isolated subagent dispatch,
# locked while the runtime owns them, removed at session end.
.claude/worktrees/

# Playwright MCP runtime dir (browser contexts / screenshots)
.playwright-mcp/

# Sprint 04 BoN fan-out smoke-test scratch dir — fork-candidate tests
# occasionally seed this; nothing in it is meant to be persisted.
benchmark/.bon-test-cache/

# Per-project visionary-kit (user-curated realism data from /visionary-kit).
# Schema + example ship under skills/visionary/schemas/ and docs/sprints/
# artifacts/; the project's own kit stays local.
/visionary-kit.json

# ─── Internal working docs (do not ship to public remotes) ───────────────
# Maintainer-only analysis briefs and scratch files. Commit-deny by pattern.
Future implementation and fixes.md
*.stackdump
bash.exe.stackdump

# ─── Node / package managers ─────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ─── OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ─── Build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
dist/
.cache/
*.tmp

# ─── ML model binaries (Sprint 11 DINOv2-small ~22 MB, etc) ──────────────
# Models are lazy-downloaded to ~/.visionary/models/ — repo never carries
# the binaries. Belt-and-suspenders here in case someone misconfigures.
*.onnx
*.gguf
*.safetensors
*.bin
models/*.onnx
models/dinov2-small.onnx
# Anchor screenshots (Sprint 11 build-anchors.mjs input) — kept local for
# size + curation provenance. Only the computed _index.json is shared.
models/style-anchors/*/*.png
models/style-anchors/*/*.jpg
models/style-anchors/*/*.jpeg

# ─── Sprint 18-19 — transformers.js / Hugging Face caches ────────────────
# CLIP ViT-B/32 (Sprint 18 from-photo) and CLAP-htsat-unfused (Sprint 19
# from-track) are ~150 MB each. They cache under node_modules/.cache/
# (covered by node_modules/) but we ignore user-level HF cache too in
# case anyone runs scripts/setup-clip-model.mjs from inside the repo.
**/.cache/huggingface/
**/.transformers-cache/
**/onnxruntime-node/
**/Xenova/

# ─── Sprint 19 — Spotify credentials (NEVER commit) ──────────────────────
# Real path is ~/.visionary/spotify-creds.json (out-of-repo). Defensive
# pattern in case anyone copies the file into the repo by mistake.
# See docs/spotify-setup.md.
**/spotify-creds.json
**/spotify-creds*.json
.visionary-secrets/

# ─── Sprint 22 — voice / audio recordings ────────────────────────────────
# Microphone recordings shouldn't land in repo. Audio test fixtures
# under hooks/scripts/lib/voice/__tests__/__fixtures__/ are explicitly
# tracked; this only ignores ad-hoc voice files in well-known scratch dirs.
voice-recordings/
*.voice.wav
*.voice.webm
# Repo-root only (not recursive) — keeps test fixtures and style-pack
# audio assets under nested dirs tracked.
/*.wav
/*.webm
/*.mp3
/*.flac
/*.ogg

# ─── Sprint 16-24 local pre-merge test scratch ───────────────────────────
# docs/local-test-1.6.0.md suggests scratch projects under ~/test-* or
# similar — those live outside this repo, but if anyone drops one inside:
local-test-*/
test-visionary-*/
.local-test/

# ─── MCP-server runtime (Sprint 10) — host installs deps locally ─────────
packages/mcp-server/node_modules/
packages/*/node_modules/
packages/*/dist/

# ─── Husky generated dirs (Sprint 14) ────────────────────────────────────
# .husky/pre-commit is committed; the _ subdir is regenerated by `npx husky`.
.husky/_/

# ─── Environment ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development
.env.production
.env.test

# ─── Secrets (defensive — Visionary itself doesn't write these) ──────────
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets.json
credentials.json
service-account*.json

# ─── IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── Claude Code local state (per-user, not plugin code) ─────────────────
.claude/
